{"tid":791571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中電(00002)在屯門龍鼓灘發電廠現沉降","createTime":"2018-08-24T01:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:43:21.000Z","uid":166434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8d42e3d2a22f7373dbcce1b2161177b0a5320ae0","tid":791571,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:36:16.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 中電(00002)在屯門龍鼓灘發電廠進行擴建燃氣機組及管道接駁工程,電廠內用作儲備石油的油鼓附近,一幅3米高的圍牆出現沉降逾28毫米,懷疑受到附近打樁工程影響,連同工地其餘兩個位置,共有三處監測點錄得沉降超標,中電一度下令停工3個月。<br />\n<br />\n中電昨證實,今年3月發現沉降監測點超標,已通知屋宇署,並已在上月獲屋宇署批出新圖則後已復工,又強調油缸與圍牆並不相連,每個油缸亦有獨立地基,該工地及附近設施安全,未受影響。而工程承建商同樣為涉及沙中線工程的禮頓。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c1223ee573746ea2abba743e9d84dd34ed138ffe","tid":791571,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"港交所停兩個鐘電會點？"},{"pid":"710434e309d35b0b16acbf79b04925a275b6453e","tid":791571,"uid":42364,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c1223ee573746ea2abba743e9d84dd34ed138ffe","tid":791571,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"港交所停兩個鐘電會點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"港島用港燈"},{"pid":"6f9d9db3f29031cc682acdcd0e43a3dc9215aa61","tid":791571,"uid":46656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"710434e309d35b0b16acbf79b04925a275b6453e","tid":791571,"uid":42364,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c1223ee573746ea2abba743e9d84dd34ed138ffe","tid":791571,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"港交所停兩個鐘電會點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"港島用港燈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f6c3fb7e8ccb208050ea1eb3830b429d2078b2","tid":791571,"uid":29773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"